msgid ""
"*dependencies.bzl*: this file tells your Bazel *WORKSPACE* how to load the "
"dependencies."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools/google/bazeldeps.rst:70
msgid ""
"*zlib/BUILD.bazel*: contains all the targets that you can load from any of "
